org.switchyard.remote

Class RemoteMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.switchyard.remote.RemoteMessage

  • @Strategy(access=FIELD)
public class RemoteMessage
extends Object
    Serializable container for context and content used in an invocation.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors

      Create an empty remote message.
      RemoteMessage(QName domain, QName service)
